📄 1. Problems Faced + Root Cause + Fix (DOCUMENT)
🔴 Problem 1 — Spring Boot & Cloud Version Conflict

Issue:

Boot → 3.5.12
Cloud → 2023.x

Reason:

Incompatible versions

Fix:

Aligned all services:
Spring Boot → 3.5.12
Spring Cloud → 2025.0.1
🔴 Problem 2 — Maven Command Wrong

Issue:

mvn spring:boot run ❌

Reason:

Wrong plugin syntax

Fix:

mvn spring-boot:run ✅
🔴 Problem 3 — Service Not Registering in Eureka

Reason:

Service not starting due to build/runtime issues

Fix:

Fixed dependencies
Fixed port conflict
Corrected configs
🔴 Problem 4 — Port Conflict

Issue:

Port 8081 already in use

Fix:

server:
  port: 9091
🔴 Problem 5 — Lombok + Constructor Conflict

Issue:

Duplicate constructor

Reason:

Used @AllArgsConstructor + manual constructor

Fix:

Removed manual constructor
🔴 Problem 6 — @Autowired + final Conflict

Issue:

@Autowired + final ❌

Fix:

Used only:
@RequiredArgsConstructor
🔴 Problem 7 — Oracle Table Creation Error

Issue:

ORA-00903: invalid table name

Reason:

user is reserved keyword

Fix:

@Table(name = "users")
🔴 Problem 8 — JWT Not Blocking Requests

Issue:

APIs accessible without token

Reason:

Filter allowed requests without header

Fix:

Enforced strict validation
🔴 Problem 9 — 403 Forbidden After JWT

Reason:

Authentication not set in Spring context

Fix:

SecurityContextHolder.getContext().setAuthentication(...)
🔴 Problem 10 — HTTP Method Confusion

Issue:

Login not working in browser

Reason:

Browser sends GET, API expects POST

Fix:

Used Postman / proper HTTP methods